INSTALL

To use this software, python >= 2.4 is needed (it should run with earlier
versions, but it hasn't been tested). See:

    http://www.python.org

To control the hardware, the following modules need to be installed:

    - pyserial: http://pyserial.sourceforge.net

Windows users needs additional modules:

    - pywin32: https://sourceforge.net/projects/pywin32

To have a 3D simulation view, vpython is required:

    - http://www.vpython.org
    
Note that vpython 3.x does not support image mapping; only vpython 4 (beta).
The program should run with both versions (with the previous limitation).

There is not installer in this panohead version (alpha). Just launch panohead.py
script in you python interpreter. Refer to you plateform python implementation.
